<i>adverb</i>: 푹신푹신 [푹씬푹씬], 푹신 [푹씬], 푸근히 [푸근히], 폭신폭신 [폭씬폭씬], 포근히 [포근히], 지그시 [지그시], 조용조용 [조용조용], 조록조록 [조록쪼록], 자근자근 [자근자근], 야들야들 [야들랴들/야드랴들], 슬슬 [슬슬], 스르륵 [스르륵], 살포시 [살포시], 살살 [살살], 살며시 [살며시], 산들산들 [산들산들], 사뿐사뿐 [사뿐사뿐], 사르르 [사르르], 뽀송뽀송 [뽀송뽀송], 부슬부슬 [부슬부슬], 부들부들 [부들부들], 보송보송 [보송보송], 물렁물렁 [물렁물렁], 말랑말랑 [말랑말랑], 나긋나긋 [나근나귿], 건들건들 [건들건들], 간들간들 [간들간들], 가만가만히 [가만가만히], 가만가만 [가만가만] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푹신푹신 [푹씬푹씬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>매우 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>Of a soft and elastic feeling in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푹신 [푹씬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly</dd><br>
<dd>조금 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A soft and elastic feeling, with comfort.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸근히 [푸근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a quite thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭신폭신 [폭씬폭씬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>매우 포근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있는 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>Of a soft and elastic feeling in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포근히 [포근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 보드랍고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 보드랍고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지그시 [지그시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>슬며시 힘을 주는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of applying pressure lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently</dd><br>
<dd>조용히 참고 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring quietly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조용조용 [조용조용]</dt><br>
<dd>quietly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 시끄럽지 않고 매우 얌전한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of not being loud and very gentle in speech or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조록조록 [조록쪼록]</dt><br>
<dd>gently; softly</dd><br>
<dd>비나 가는 물줄기 등이 빠르게 자꾸 내리거나 흐르는 소리 또는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a sound resembling one that is produced when rain or a narrow stream of water falls down quickly and continuously, or such an action.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자근자근 [자근자근]</dt><br>
<dd>1. annoyingly</dd><br>
<dd>괴로울 정도로 자꾸 귀찮게 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of annoying someone so much as to make him/her feel pain.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>자꾸 가볍게 누르거나 밟는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing or stepping on something lightly and continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>3. nibble nibble</dd><br>
<dd>자꾸 가볍게 씹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of chewing something lightly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>야들야들 [야들랴들/야드랴들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. softly; delicately</dd><br>
<dd>반들반들 윤기가 돌고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being glossy and smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>목소리 등이 맑고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's voice, etc., being clear and tender.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>슬슬 [슬슬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slowly</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 천천히 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly, not hastening.</dd><br>
<dd>8. effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘들이지 않고 쉽게 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing something easily without much effort.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>스르륵 [스르륵]</dt><br>
<dd>softly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 물건이 바닥이나 다른 물건에 스치면서 부드럽게 나는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the soft sound or describing the movement of something scraping against a floor or another thing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살포시 [살포시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently; softly</dd><br>
<dd>포근하게 살며시.</dd><br>
<dd>In a snug and discreet manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>남의 눈에 뜨지 않게 살짝.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a stealthy manner that it does not attract attention.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>얽힌 실 등이 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of tangled thread, etc., disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살며시 [살며시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르도록 조용히 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and carefully so that others do not notice.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly; softly; cautiously</dd><br>
<dd>천천히 가볍고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a slow, light, and careful manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>산들산들 [산들산들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. softly</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 시원하고 부드럽게 자꾸 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of the refreshing wind blowing gently.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>물건이 바람에 가볍고 부드럽게 자꾸 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of something being swayed lightly and gently by the wind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사뿐사뿐 [사뿐사뿐]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>소리가 나지 않도록 가볍게 계속해서 걷는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of walking with soft steps so that it does not make a sound.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 계속해서 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving continuously and lightly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사르르 [사르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. of itself</dd><br>
<dd>얽히거나 뭉쳤던 것이 저절로 부드럽게 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that something tangled or lumped is gently disentangled by itself.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in the manner of melting away</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 얼음 등이 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner in which snow, ice, etc., melt naturally.</dd><br>
<dd>3. unconsciously</dd><br>
<dd>졸음이나 어떤 분위기에 살며시 빠져드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of falling asleep or quietly slipping into a certain mood.</dd><br>
<dd>4. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 살며시 감거나 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of opening or closing one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>5. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>살며시 조용하게 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving stealthily and quietly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. tremblingly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 힘없이 떨리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of trembling lightly and feebly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>배 등 몸의 일부가 조금씩 아픈 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a part of one's body such as the stomach aches a little.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>뽀송뽀송 [뽀송뽀송]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in a dry and tender state</dd><br>
<dd>잘 말라서 물기가 없고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being dried yet soft.</dd><br>
<dd>2. smoothly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부나 얼굴이 곱고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's skin or face is soft and smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fuzzily; downily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 작고 보드라운 털 같은 것이 돋아 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of having very short, soft hair or something similar.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부슬부슬 [부슬부슬]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>비나 눈이 조금씩 조용히 내리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of rain or snow falling lightly and quietly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부들부들 [부들부들]</dt><br>
<dd>softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부에 닿는 느낌이 매우 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a feeling to the skin is very smooth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>보송보송 [보송보송]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in a dry and soft state</dd><br>
<dd>잘 말라서 물기가 없고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being smooth and having dried well without moisture.</dd><br>
<dd>2. softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부나 얼굴이 곱고 보드라운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's skin or face is fair and smooth.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in small beads</dd><br>
<dd>땀방울이 조금씩 솟은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which sweat is excreted in small amounts, here and there.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fuzzily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 작고 보드라운 털 같은 것이 돋아 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which very small, soft tufts of hair or the like have grown on something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>물렁물렁 [물렁물렁]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; mushily</dd><br>
<dd>매우 부드럽고 무른 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling very smooth and squashy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>말랑말랑 [말랑말랑]</dt><br>
<dd>softly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 보들보들하여 연하고 부드러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a feeling as being smooth, tender, and soft.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>나긋나긋 [나근나귿]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smoothly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>피부로 전해지는 느낌이 매우 연하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling soft and mild on the skin.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mildly; amiably</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 태도가 매우 상냥하고 부드러운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a very kind and soft personality or attitude.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>건들건들 [건들건들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently; softly</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 자꾸 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of the wind blowing lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. impertinently; impolitely</dd><br>
<dd>태도가 바르지 않고 건방지게 구는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With an impolite and impudent attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>3. idly; lazily</dd><br>
<dd>하는 일이 없거나 성실하지 않아 게으름을 피우는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of dawdling because one has nothing to do or because one is lazy.</dd><br>
<dd>4. waveringly</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 이리저리 가볍게 자꾸 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of a small object swaying back and forth gently.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>간들간들 [간들간들]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently; softly</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of the wind blowing lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. impudently; impertinently</dd><br>
<dd>태도가 바르지 않고 조금 건방지게 구는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With an impolite and impudent attitude.</dd><br>
<dd>3. waveringly</dd><br>
<dd>작은 물체가 이리저리 가볍게 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of a small object swaying gently back and forth.</dd><br>
<dd>4. danglingly</dd><br>
<dd>위태롭게 매달려 힘들게 붙어 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of something hanging dangerously.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가만가만히 [가만가만히]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>아주 조용하고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very quietly and carefully.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가만가만 [가만가만]</dt><br>
<dd>softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>아주 조용하고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very quietly and carefully.</dd><br>
